{"name":"效率工具","postlist":[{"title":"gopic配置七牛云图床","slug":"tools/qiniuandgopic","date":"2024-07-20T02:24:16.000Z","updated":"2026-06-22T13:56:52.761Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/tools/qiniuandgopic.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":"VLA,VLM,机器人,具身智能,仿真数据,Real2Sim,Simulation Data,Embodied AI,Robotics","cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Longtao-W/pics@main/24/160240244227154224703112850174179347216207_gopic_.png","content":"<h2 id=\"创建七牛云存储（已经存在可以跳过）\"><a href=\"#创建七牛云存储（已经存在可以跳过）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建七牛云存储（已经存在可以跳过）\"></a>创建七牛云存储（已经存在可以跳过）</h2><ol>\n<li>注册登录七牛云<a href=\"https://s.qiniu.com/UBzmey\">https://s.qiniu.com/UBzmey</a></li>\n<li>点击秘钥管理，获取ak和sk</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Longtao-W/pics@main/23/252108234243995602521195377126111816208_gopic_.png\" alt=\"image-20230625144220185\"></p>\n<p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Longtao-W/pics@main/23/202127149222217237139517275595124320624215_gopic_.png\" alt=\"image-20230625144305819\"></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><p>创建存储桶，注意选择公开访问</p>\n<p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Longtao-W/pics@main/23/8212513862222472293925122319720315521587133_gopic_.png\" alt=\"image-20230625144445633\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>创建成功后可以选择绑定自定义域名，也可以使用测试域名(测试域名只能用1个月)<br><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Longtao-W/pics@main/23/222141732119970281958617521766118170125235_gopic_.png\" alt=\"image-20230625144621858\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>这里我们直接绑定域名</p>\n<p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Longtao-W/pics@main/23/124180132741128624818061721733617664150104_gopic_.png\" alt=\"image-20230625145205806\"></p>\n<p>注意：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>加速域名：指用户提供的需要使用CDN加速服务的域名，即终端用户访问的域名。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>源站域名：指服务器IP地址对应的域名，即CDN回源时访问的域名</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>两种至少配置一种，其中cdn加速是收费的</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><p>加速域名设置详见：<a href=\"https://developer.qiniu.com/kodo/8555/set-the-custom-cdn-to-accelerate-the-domain-name\">https://developer.qiniu.com/kodo/8555/set-the-custom-cdn-to-accelerate-the-domain-name</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>源站域名设置详见<a href=\"https://developer.qiniu.com/kodo/8556/set-the-custom-source-domain-name\">https://developer.qiniu.com/kodo/8556/set-the-custom-source-domain-name</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>我这里只配置了cdn加速域名(配置了两个)<br><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Longtao-W/pics@main/23/2364116793271192422912215129961822559020_gopic_.png\" alt=\"image-20230625145416921\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>配置完成后使用域名获取对象存储中的资源成功即配置成功</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"配置gopic\"><a href=\"#配置gopic\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置gopic\"></a>配置gopic</h2><ol>\n<li>安装完gopic后，运行<code>gopic conf</code>获取配置文件位置</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Longtao-W/pics@main/23/2652535273361642252521311211532516414852_gopic_.png\" alt=\"image-20230625145750771\"></p>\n<p>我这里是在<code>/home/longtao/.gopic.json</code></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>打开文件</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Longtao-W/pics@main/23/20159243407315220584401179314502462211_gopic_.png\" alt=\"image-20230625150021810\"></p>\n<p>在配置中添加</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">&quot;qiniu&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;active&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"literal\"><span class=\"keyword\">true</span></span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"comment\">//是否激活</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;accessKey&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;你的七牛云ak&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;secretKey&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;你的七牛云sk&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;bucket&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;你的七牛云空间名称&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;responseURL&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Longtao-W/pics@main/&quot;</span> <span class=\"comment\">//你配置的域名+/pics/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>打开typora的偏好设置</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Longtao-W/pics@main/23/1162559210534150114126221261756918219848173_gopic_.png\" alt=\"image-20230625150321187\"></p>\n<p>修改图像中的配置，gopic中使用命令<code>gopic upload -s qiniu  -f qiniu -p</code></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>点击验证图片上传选项验证是否成功</li>\n</ol>\n","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"创作工具","path":"api/categories/创作工具.json"},{"name":"创作工具/tool","path":"api/categories/创作工具/tool.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"编程工具","path":"api/tags/编程工具.json"},{"name":"效率工具","path":"api/tags/效率工具.json"}]}]}